HEADHUNTER: Professional mercenary soldier for hire

The Headhunter is a professional mercenary soldier: skilled, heavily
armed, and for hire to anyone who can afford the rate. They are among
the best non-Coalition soldiers on Rifts Earth.

Headhunters begin with a strong military skill base including
demolitions, two vehicle specializations, and multiple weapon
proficiencies. They choose from Espionage, Military, Physical, Pilot,
Technical, and W.P. categories.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: PS 10, PE 10.
  Equipment: Body armor, two modern ranged weapons, one melee weapon,
    combat knife, radio communicator, and mercenary ID papers.

